Capital Markets

Company Overview of Elliott International Ltd



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Elliott International Ltd is a hedge fund limited partnership launched and managed by Elliott Management Corporation. The fund invests in public equity and hedging markets. It diversifies its investments across bonds, foreign exchange, warrants, options, and futures. The fund primarily invests in distressed companies, such as those in bankruptcy, undergoing reorganization or corporate restructuring. Elliott International Ltd is domiciled in the United States.


40 West 57th StreetNew York, NY 10019United States



Phone: 212-974-6000

Fax: 212-478-2476








