            Business Description
        



Elliott International L.p is located in New York, New York. This organization primarily operates in the Management Services business / industry within the Engineering, Accounting, Research, and Management Services sector. This organization has been operating for approximately 11 years. Elliott International L.p is estimated to generate $190,000 in annual revenues, and employs approximately 2 people at this single location.









